<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 12:10:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“他们讨厌我们的硬件”：乌克兰称这对主要城市附近的俄罗斯人“释放地狱”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/they-hate-our-hardware-ukraine-says-its-unleashing-hell-on-russians-near-key-city/articleshow/103890146.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103890146.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰表示，在5月份被俄罗斯占领的巴赫穆特郊区的激烈战斗中，乌克兰使用了西方提供的重型武器，正在严重影响敌人的阵地。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 11:37:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/they-hate-our-hardware-ukraine-says-its-unleashing-hell-on-russians-near-key-city/articleshow/103890146.cms</guid></item><item><title>联邦政府即将关闭。这意味着什么？谁被击中了，接下来会发生什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-federal-government-is-headed-into-a-shutdown-what-does-it-mean-whos-hit-and-whats-next/articleshow/103888800.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103888800.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于众议院共和党人推动大幅削减联邦支出，联邦政府正处于关闭的边缘。关闭将导致非必要的政府工作暂停、联邦雇员工资延迟以及政府服务中断。全国各地的军事人员、文职人员和联邦办公室都将受到影响。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 10:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-federal-government-is-headed-into-a-shutdown-what-does-it-mean-whos-hit-and-whats-next/articleshow/103888800.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩军队从黎巴嫩海岸附近沉船中救出27名移民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanese-troops-rescue-27-migrants-from-sinking-boat-off-lebanons-coast/articleshow/103888605.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103888605.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;黎巴嫩军方在一份声明中表示，周六早些时候，黎巴嫩军队和民防部门驱逐了27名在黎巴嫩北部海岸附近沉船的移民。军方没有透露移民的目的地，也没有透露他们的国籍。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 10:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanese-troops-rescue-27-migrants-from-sinking-boat-off-lebanons-coast/articleshow/103888605.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国逮捕并指控卢旺达前官员参与1994年种族灭绝：消息来源</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-arrests-charges-rwanda-ex-official-over-1994-genocide-source/articleshow/103888130.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103888130.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周六，一位知情人士称，法国本周逮捕并指控了一名前卢旺达地区高级官员，罪名是该国 1994 年的种族灭绝事件。基布耶地区省长、前议员皮埃尔·卡永多于周二被捕，并被指控犯有种族灭绝罪和反人类罪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 10:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-arrests-charges-rwanda-ex-official-over-1994-genocide-source/articleshow/103888130.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰导弹袭击了俄罗斯克里米亚海军总部</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-ukrainian-missile-strikes-the-headquarters-of-russias-navy-in-crimea/articleshow/103886198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103886198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰对俄罗斯黑海舰队克里米亚总部发动导弹袭击，造成一名军人失踪，并对大楼造成损坏。 2014年被俄罗斯吞并的克里米亚一直是乌克兰与俄罗斯持续冲突的目标。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 08:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-ukrainian-missile-strikes-the-headquarters-of-russias-navy-in-crimea/articleshow/103886198.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：伊斯兰堡高等法院确定伊姆兰·汗密码案保释请求听证会的日期</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-islamabad-high-court-fixes-date-for-imran-khans-bail-plea-hearing-in-cipher-case/articleshow/103885211.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103885211.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊斯兰堡高等法院已安排就前总理伊姆兰·汗在密码案中提出的逮捕后保释申请举行听证会。法院已向联邦调查局（FIA）发出通知，就该案进行辩论。特别法庭此前驳回了汗及其政党副主席沙阿·马哈茂德·库雷希的保释请求。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 07:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-islamabad-high-court-fixes-date-for-imran-khans-bail-plea-hearing-in-cipher-case/articleshow/103885211.cms</guid></item><item><title>意大利前总统、第一位前共产党员乔治·纳波利塔诺 (Giorgio Napolitano) 去世，享年 98 岁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/giorgio-napolitano-former-italian-president-and-1st-ex-communist-in-that-post-has-died-at-98/articleshow/103885149.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103885149.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔治·纳波利塔诺 (Giorgio Napolitano) 是首位成为意大利总统的前共产党人，现已去世，享年 98 岁。纳波利塔诺曾两度担任总统，以其改革主义观点和结束政党孤立的努力而闻名。教皇方济各称赞他的才智和对意大利政治生活的热情。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 07:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/giorgio-napolitano-former-italian-president-and-1st-ex-communist-in-that-post-has-died-at-98/articleshow/103885149.cms</guid></item><item><title>泰国反对党前进党任命新领导人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailands-opposition-move-forward-party-names-new-leader/articleshow/103884962.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103884962.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在前领导人皮塔·林贾伦拉 (Pita Limjaroenrat) 竞选泰国总理失败后，泰国反对党前进党 (Move Forward) 任命猜泰瓦·图拉通 (Chaithawat Tulathon) 为其新领导人。在五月选举中赢得议会最多席位的前进党现在将成为主要反对党。由于法律和立法方面的挑战，Limjaroenrat 本月早些时候辞职。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 07:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailands-opposition-move-forward-party-names-new-leader/articleshow/103884962.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称亚美尼亚分裂分子在阿塞拜疆收复纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫后交出武器</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-says-armenian-separatists-surrender-arms-after-azerbaijan-reclaims-nagorno-karabakh/articleshow/103883887.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103883887.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在阿塞拜疆收复分离地区后，纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫的亚美尼亚分裂分子已向俄罗斯维和人员交出武器。分离主义团体交出了装甲车、轻武器和弹药。关于将该地区重新纳入阿塞拜疆的谈判正在进行中，而俄罗斯正在调查两起违反停火事件。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 06:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-says-armenian-separatists-surrender-arms-after-azerbaijan-reclaims-nagorno-karabakh/articleshow/103883887.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国反对党领袖结束24天绝食</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-opposition-leader-ends-24-day-hunger-strike/articleshow/103883498.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103883498.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国反对党领袖李在明结束了24天的绝食。此前，议会投票允许检察官以涉嫌贿赂的罪名对他发出逮捕令。韩国民主党领袖李在镕将在住院期间继续出庭。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 06:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-opposition-leader-ends-24-day-hunger-strike/articleshow/103883498.cms</guid></item><item><title>被围困地带的巴勒斯坦人向以色列发射燃烧气球后，以色列袭击了加沙</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-strikes-gaza-after-palestinians-in-besieged-strip-launch-incendiary-balloons-toward-israel/articleshow/103883244.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103883244.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴勒斯坦活动人士向以色列境内释放燃烧气球后，以色列对加沙地带发动空袭，导致动荡的边境紧张局势升级。被占领的约旦河西岸的暴力事件也激增，以色列军队杀死了一名巴勒斯坦武装分子。巴勒斯坦抗议者一直在加沙以色列围栏附近示威，向以色列军队投掷爆炸物，以色列军队以催泪瓦斯和实弹回应。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 06:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-strikes-gaza-after-palestinians-in-besieged-strip-launch-incendiary-balloons-toward-israel/articleshow/103883244.cms</guid></item><item><title>岛国在联合国大会上指责富裕国家在气候问题上无所作为</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/island-nations-blame-rich-countries-for-climate-inaction-at-un-assembly/articleshow/103879610.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103879610.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;受气候变化影响的岛国在联合国大会上批评发达国家在解决这一问题上缺乏紧迫感。未能遏制温室气体排放导致海平面上升，对这些国家构成威胁。发言者强调，需要根据《巴黎协定》的规定，采取行动将全球变暖限制在 1.5 摄氏度之内。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 03:11:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/island-nations-blame-rich-countries-for-climate-inaction-at-un-assembly/articleshow/103879610.cms</guid></item><item><title>加拿大反对党领袖谴责针对印度教徒的“仇恨言论”，强调他们的“宝贵贡献”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadas-opposition-leader-condemns-hateful-comments-targeting-hindus-highlights-their-invaluable-contribution/articleshow/103879224.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103879224.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加拿大反对党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫谴责该国针对印度教徒的“仇恨言论”，并表示印度教徒为加拿大做出了宝贵贡献。此前，一个亲卡利斯坦组织的负责人威胁印度裔印度教徒，并要求他们离开加拿大。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 02:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadas-opposition-leader-condemns-hateful-comments-targeting-hindus-highlights-their-invaluable-contribution/articleshow/103879224.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼基·黑利：中国对美国构成生存威胁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/china-an-existential-threat-to-us-nikki-haley/articleshow/103879356.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103879356.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度裔美国共和党总统候选人尼基·黑利将中国称为对美国和国际社会的“生存威胁”。她在施政报告中表示，中国花了50年的时间谋划超越美国，中国的军队已经与美国武装力量不相上下。黑利指责中国窃取制造业就业机会和商业机密，并意图主宰亚洲。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 02:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/china-an-existential-threat-to-us-nikki-haley/articleshow/103879356.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾对中国演习局势“失控”表示担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-raises-concerns-about-situation-getting-out-of-hand-with-china-drills/articleshow/103879018.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103879018.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾国防部长对中国在台湾附近增加军事活动表示担忧，并警告可能发生意外冲突。台湾报告称，过去两周出现了数十架中国战斗机、无人机、轰炸机、军舰和山东舰。中国一直在进行此类演习，以维护其主权主张并向台湾施压。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Sep 2023 02:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-raises-concerns-about-situation-getting-out-of-hand-with-china-drills/articleshow/103879018.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦记者因传播“反国家”言论被捕，被国际汽联还押两天</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/journalist-in-pakistan-arrested-for-spreading-anti-state-narrative-remanded-in-fia-custody-for-two-days/articleshow/103877695.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103877695.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;记者穆罕默德·哈立德·贾米尔已被伊斯兰堡法院还押两天。他因被指控通过社交媒体帖子散布针对国家机构的挑衅性言论而被捕。联邦调查局（FIA）指控贾米尔分享恐吓内容和虚假信息，可能煽动危害国家或公共安宁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 23:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/journalist-in-pakistan-arrested-for-spreading-anti-state-narrative-remanded-in-fia-custody-for-two-days/articleshow/103877695.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国外科医生进行第二次猪心脏移植手术，试图挽救垂死的男子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-surgeons-perform-second-pig-heart-transplant-trying-to-save-a-dying-man/articleshow/103877624.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103877624.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马里兰州的外科医生成功地将猪心脏移植到一个垂死的人身上，这是第二次进行这样的手术。这位58岁的患者不适合接受传统的心脏移植手术，但在手术后仅两天就出现了积极的康复迹象。此次移植手术是由去年进行世界首例转基因猪心脏移植手术的同一团队进行的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 23:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-surgeons-perform-second-pig-heart-transplant-trying-to-save-a-dying-man/articleshow/103877624.cms</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，2022 年英格兰将有 4,500 多人因高温死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/england-saw-4500-heat-linked-deaths-in-2022-study/articleshow/103877600.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103877600.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国国家统计局 (ONS) 发表的一项研究显示，英格兰与高温相关的死亡人数有所增加，预计 2022 年将有 4,507 人死亡。ONS 警告称，该数据是实验性的，建议不要进行逐年比较。研究还显示，英国有记录以来最热的10年都发生在21世纪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 23:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/england-saw-4500-heat-linked-deaths-in-2022-study/articleshow/103877600.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国与蒙古和俄罗斯经济走廊试验高速公路</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-trials-highway-in-economic-corridor-with-mongolia-russia/articleshow/103877573.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103877573.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据中国官方媒体报道，一支由九辆卡车组成的车队于周五离开中国西北部的新疆前往新西伯利亚，试验一条雄心勃勃的跨国高速公路，这是中国、蒙古和俄罗斯设想的更广泛经济走廊的关键路线。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 23:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-trials-highway-in-economic-corridor-with-mongolia-russia/articleshow/103877573.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯计划大幅增加国防预算</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-planning-big-hike-in-defence-budget/articleshow/103877539.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/103877539.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据彭博社周五报道，俄罗斯计划明年大幅增加国防开支，占 GDP 的比重从 2023 年的 3.9% 和 2021 年的 2.7% 增至 6%。随着乌克兰战争成本急剧上升，给莫斯科的财政带来越来越大的压力，莫斯科将 2023 年国防开支目标翻了一番，达到 1000 亿美元以上。政府定于周五讨论预算提案草案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 23:00:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-planning-big-hike-in-defence-budget/articleshow/103877539.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>